{"tid":2007092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於認罪手足我有一個想法","createTime":"2020-05-08T07:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T09:47:51.000Z","uid":182907,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc3f5951f2ac0f289e5e9a4a1a97ce63e8c70eb","tid":2007092,"uid":182907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"出圖先講野 唔好話我得個講字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有得揀 冇人想坐監</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n但現實啲狗有幾仆街大家都知<br />\n從被捕嗰一刻去到上法庭 當中會經歷好多既折磨 無論係心理上定係生理上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可能未必明白，<br />\n當你睇到一張又一張清過屋企電視嘅CCTV cap圖 <br />\n其實真係再冇希望呢兩個字<br />\n但冇希望嘅並唔係未來 我哋依然相信未來係有大家一齊撐住， 只係我哋需要短暫嘅離開 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認罪唔係傻仔，只係想快啲歸隊</span></span>"},{"pid":"0634b1b82826bb7e337d2ccec35211acf1c9f90f","tid":2007092,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:36:48.000Z","msg":"冇份坐果d 收收皮先"},{"pid":"4118db224171be11953b3c826cb37e16eb44e3fa","tid":2007092,"uid":114792,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:40:32.000Z","msg":"傻啦<br />\n得自己會為自己落最好嘅決定<br />\n唔係歸唔歸隊嘅問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed2363d6f12c95848c87fa6850cf52de3fc1f0d","tid":2007092,"uid":285371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:42:35.000Z","msg":"唔好理失敗撚<br />\n從來都係winner takes all<br />\n加油, 大家團火唔會無左"},{"pid":"bbf8f91d40b0be0675efd0cb1bde2dc7a54abb8f","tid":2007092,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e46efdec3d3b67d20cdd39254217743635117c9d","tid":2007092,"uid":182907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf8f91d40b0be0675efd0cb1bde2dc7a54abb8f","tid":2007092,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dis